INSERT INTO `offices` VALUES (1,'Glumangate ','24 Glumangate\r\nChesterfield\r\nDerbyshire ','S40 1UA','01246 560560','<h3>From  Sheffield</h3>\r\n<p>Take the A61 (Dual carriageway) to Chesterfield. Stay on this  road  until you come to the large roundabout with Tesco&rsquo;s on your left hand   side.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Go straight across at this  roundabout and after 1 mile take the slip road A632 sign posted  Chesterfield/Matlock/Bolsover.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>At the  lights turn left, under the bridge to the roundabout and then turn right sign  posted Town Centre.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Follow the road up  the hill through two sets of lights past the Crooked Spire on the left, to the  lights.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Keep in the right hand lane but  go straight on leaving Eyres on your left hand side.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Up to the next lights and again go straight  on.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Stay on this road called Saltergate  for&nbsp; 250 yards (Co-Op on your left hand  side) and Glumangate is on your left hand side.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Turn left at the lights and our office is on  the right hand side.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you are driving  (as Glumangate is a one way street) take the  second turning on your left (after  Glumangate) on to Rose Hill.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>At the  bottom turn left onto Knifesmithgate and Glumangate is the second on the left  hand side.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Turn left and we are 50  yards up on the left hand side.</p>\r\n<p><em>There is limited parking outside the office  (maximum of 20 minutes for 50 pence).<br /> More car parking can be seen on the maps.</em></p>\r\n<p><em>For  Example</em></p>\r\n<p><em>Car parking in the Town Hall is 80p for up  to 1 hour, &pound;1.80 for up to 2 hours.</em></p>\r\n<h3>From  Junction 29 of the Motorway</h3>\r\n<p>Follow the dual carriageway towards Chesterfield and at the  end you will come to a roundabout.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Go  straight across sign posted Town Centre/Buxton/Bakewell to the  next roundabout  and go straight across sign posted Town Centre.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Follow the road up the hill through two  sets of lights, past the Crooked Spire on the left, to the lights.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Keep in right hand lane and go straight on  leaving Eyres on the left hand side.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Up  to the next lights and again go straight on.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Stay on this road called Saltergate for 250 yards (Co-Op on your left  hand side) and Glumangate is on your left hand side.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you are driving (as Glumangate is a one  way street) take the second on your left (after Glumgate) onto Rose Hill.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>At the bottom turn left onto Knifesmithgate  and Glumangate is the second on the right hand side.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Turn left and we are 50 yards up on the left  hand side.</p>\r\n<p><em>There is limited parking outside the office  (maximum 20 minutes for 50 pence).<br /> More car parking can be seen on the maps.</em></p>\r\n<p><em>For  Example</em></p>\r\n<p><em>Car parking in the Town Hall is 80p for up  to 1 hour, &pound;1.80 for up to 2 hours.</em></p>\r\n<h3>From  Derby/Clay Cross/Alfreton</h3>\r\n<p>You will approach Chesterfield on the A61 (Derby Road) and will see on your right  hand side at the lights MacDonalds.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Go  straight across to the roundabout and turn left sign posted Town Centre.</p>\r\n<p>Follow the road up the hill through two  sets of lights past the Crooked Spire on the left, to the lights.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Keep in the right hand lane and go straight  on leaving Eyres on the left hand side.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Up to the next lights and again go straight on.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Stay on this road Saltergate for 250 yards  (Co-Op on your left hand side) and Glumangate is on your left hand side.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Our office is 100 yards down on the right  hand side.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you are driving (as Glumangate is a one  way street) take the  second turning on your left (after Glumangate) on to Rose  Hill.</p>\r\n<p>At the bottom turn left onto Knifesmithgate  and Glumangate is the  second on the left hand side. Turn left and we are 50  yards up on the  left hand side.</p>\r\n<p><em>There is limited parking outside the office  (maximum 20 minutes for 50 pence).<br /> More car parking can be seen on the maps. </em></p>\r\n<p><em>For  Example</em></p>\r\n<p><em>Car parking in the Town Hall park is 80p  for up to 1 hour, &pound;1.80 for up to 2 hours.</em></p>\r\n<h3>From  Junction 30&nbsp; (or Brimington/Staveley) to  Gluman Gate.</h3>\r\n<p>From the motorway follow A616 to Chesterfield.&nbsp; Do not turn off this road.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Go through Staveley and Brimington, past  the cemetery on the left  hand side, to the roundabout (Sainsburys on right hand  side) and filter  left.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To the next  roundabout and turn left onto the dual carriageway ( do not take the first left  as this takes you into Tesco&rsquo;s).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>After 1  mile take the slip road A632 sign posted Chesterfield/Matlock/Bolsover.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>At the lights turn left, under the bridge to  the roundabout and turn right sign posted Town Centre.</p>\r\n<p>Follow the road up the hill through two  sets of lights past the Crooked Spire on the left, to the lights.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Keep in the right hand lane and go straight  on leaving Eyres on the left hand side.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Up to the next lights and again go straight on.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Stay on this road called Saltergate for 250  yards (Co-Op on your left hand side) and Glumangate is on your left hand  side.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you are driving (as Glumangate  is a one way street) take the  second turning on your left (after Glumangate) on  to Rose Hill.</p>\r\n<p><em>For  Example</em></p>\r\n<p><em>Car parking in the Town Hall park is 80p  for up to 1 hour, &pound;1.80 for up to 2 hours.</em></p>\r\n<h3>For  Gluman Gate</h3>\r\n<p>Take the A619 to Chesterfield.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>On approaching Chesterfield,  the first roundabout you go straight  across (Morrisons will be on your right  hand side) and keep following  this &ldquo;Chatsworth    Road&rdquo; into Chesterfield.</p>\r\n<p>You will come to a one way system and  B&amp;Q will be on your right hand side.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>At the traffic lights you want to be in the middle lane, so that you  can  turn left in 100 yards between the shops into Rutland Road.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Follow the road up the hill to the lights  and turn right onto Saltergate.</p>\r\n<p>Follow for 450 yards and Glumangate is on  your right hand side.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Our offices are a  100 yards down the right hand side.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>As  this is a one street, if you are arriving by car from Saltergate  you need to turn  right immediately after the Town Hall into Rose  Hill.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>At the bottom turn left onto Knifesmithgate  and Glumangate is the second on the left hand side.</p>\r\n<p><em>There is limited parking outside the office  (maximum 20 minutes for 50 pence).&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em> More  car parking can be seen on the maps.</em></p>\r\n<p><em>For  Example</em></p>\r\n<p><em>Car parking in the Town Hall is 80p for up  to 1 hour, &pound;1.80 for up to 2 hours.</em></p>','2011-01-19 09:33:26','2011-04-01 14:32:34',1,1,0,NULL,1,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(2,'Glumangate (Accident Claim Centre)','26 Glumangate\r\nChesterfield\r\nDerbyshire','S40 1UA','01246 560560','<h3>From  Sheffield</h3>\r\n<p>Take the A61 (Dual carriageway) to Chesterfield. Stay on this  road   until you come to the large roundabout with Tesco&rsquo;s on your left hand    side.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Go straight across at this  roundabout and after 1 mile take the slip road A632 sign posted  Chesterfield/Matlock/Bolsover.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>At the  lights turn left, under the bridge to the roundabout and then turn right sign  posted Town Centre.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Fo