low for 450 yards and Glumangate is on  your right hand side.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Our offices are a  100 yards down the right hand side.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>As  this is a one street, if you are arriving by car from Saltergate   you need to turn  right immediately after the Town Hall into Rose   Hill.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>At the bottom turn left onto Knifesmithgate  and Glumangate is the second on the left hand side.</p>\r\n<p><em>There is limited parking outside the office  (maximum 20 minutes for 50 pence).&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></p>\r\n<p><em> More  car parking can be seen on the maps.</em></p>\r\n<p><em>For  Example</em></p>\r\n<p><em>Car parking in the Town Hall is 80p for up  to 1 hour, &pound;1.80 for up to 2 hours.</em></p>','2011-01-21 10:57:49','2011-04-01 14:32:43',1,1,0,NULL,1,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(3,'Bolsover','4 Cotton Street\r\nBolsover\r\nChesterfield\r\nDerbyshire ','S44 6HA','01246 827516','<h3>From  Chesterfield</h3>\r\n<p>Take the A632 into Boslover.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You will approach via a steep hill (Station Road).&nbsp; You will see the Market Place on the right  hand side and our office is just after this on Cotton Street.</p>\r\n<p><em>Parking is free in the car park just past  the Co-Op on the left hand side.</em></p>\r\n<h3>From  Shirebrook/Sherwood/Ollerton</h3>\r\n<p>Come into Bolsover on the A632, to the main  roundabout and then turn left into the centre.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Our office is on the left hand side just before the Market Place, half  way down Cotton Street.</p>\r\n<p><em>Parking is free in the car park just before  the Co-Op on the right hand side.</em></p>','2011-01-19 09:43:50','2011-04-01 14:32:52',1,1,0,NULL,1,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(4,'Dronfield','1 Sheffield Road\r\nDronfield\r\nDerbyshire','S18 2DH','01246 414438','<h3>From  Chesterfield</h3>\r\n<p>Take the A61 towards Sheffield, go straight  on at the roundabout (the Little Chef is on the right hand side), towards Sheffield.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Take  the first slip road off for Sheepbridge Trading Estate.&nbsp; At the T junction turn right towards  Dronfield.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Once in Dronfield follow the  Sheffield signs.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>On exiting you will see our office on the  right hand side after the station.</p>\r\n<h3>From  Sheffield</h3>\r\n<p>Follow the dual carriage way (A61) from  Sheffield towards Chesterfield,  past the Moat House Hotel (on the left hand side) the next roundabout and take  the second left towards Dronfield.</p>\r\n<p>Just before you arrive at Dronfield you  will see Little Italy on the left hand side and Sheaf Motors on the right hand  side.</p>\r\n<p>Straight over the small roundabout and our  office is on the left hand side just before the Station turning.</p>\r\n<p><em>Parking</em></p>\r\n<p><em>Limited parking outside the office.&nbsp;&nbsp; Parking also available in the Station car park.&nbsp; All free.</em></p>','2011-01-19 09:45:56','2011-04-01 14:32:58',1,1,0,NULL,1,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(5,'Clay Cross','95 High Street\r\nClay Cross\r\nChesterfield\r\nDerbyshire','S45 9DZ','01246 861250','<h3>From  Chesterfield</h3>\r\n<p>From Chesterfield  &ndash; take the A61 sign posted Derby/Alfreton/Clay Cross.</p>\r\n<p>On approaching Clay Cross Centre you will  come to a set of pedestrian traffic lights.</p>\r\n<p>Market Street will be on your left hand  side.&nbsp; Our office is on the corner by  Wilkins &amp; Vardy on the High Street directly opposite the North East  Derbyshire Social Centre</p>\r\n<h3>From  Alfreton/Derby</h3>\r\n<p>Take the A61 and continue until you come  into Clay Cross.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>You will go past the  church on the left hand side and our office is down the side of Wilkins Vardy  on the left hand side.</p>\r\n<p><em>There is very limited parking outside the  office, there is a car park opposite The Soapbox and Kwik Save just off Market Street (free  parking).</em></p>','2011-01-19 09:48:00','2011-04-01 14:33:08',1,1,0,NULL,1,0,NULL,NUL