s (Co-Op on your  left hand side) and Marsden Street is on your right hand  side.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Our office is on the corner of Marsden Street and  Saltergate just after the pedestrian crossing.</p>\r\n<p><em>For  Example</em></p>\r\n<p><em>Car parking in the Town Hall park is 80p  for up to 1 hour, &pound;1.80 for up to 2&nbsp;  hours.</em></p>','2011-01-19 09:40:09','2011-04-01 14:33:22',1,1,0,NULL,1,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
