head\"><span class=\"alt\">We are experts in</span> <span>Road Traffic Accident claims</span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"subhead\">Road Traffic Accidents are one of the most common cause of personal injury so if you or a family member have been unfortunate enough to have been injured in&nbsp;a road traffic accident, through no fault of your own, we can&nbsp;help you. &nbsp;Our&nbsp;team of specialist&nbsp;solicitors will be able to advise you on your<strong>&nbsp;</strong>claim whether you were on foot, in a car, or an a motorbike&nbsp;or bike.</p>\r\n<p class=\"subhead\">We can offer you help with simple bruising and whiplash claims, through to representation of more serious or even fatal accidents.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"c3060\" class=\"csc\">\r\n<div class=\"content\">Our solicitors are experienced in assessing road traffic claims for accidents involving:</div>\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Car drivers</li>\r\n<li>Passengers</li>\r\n<li>Cyclists</li>\r\n<li>Pedestrians</li>\r\n<li>Public Transport</li>\r\n<li>Motorcyclists</li>\r\n<li>Claims against the Motor Insurers Bureau (MIB)</li>\r\n<li>Overseas RTAs</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>We can advise you on your injuries and any financial losses incurred. <br /><br />If you have been seriously injured in a road traffic accident, we do everything we can to ensure you have easy access to additional support and advice on issues such as employment, benefit and welfare rights.<br /><br />We can also consider whether interim payments of compensation may be available to relieve financial pressures and cover immediate expenses.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Uninsured motorist</h2>\r\n<p>If your injuries were caused by the negligent driving of an uninsured motorist, your claim could be referred to the Motor Insurers Bureau under the &ldquo;Uninsured Drivers Agreement&rdquo;. MIB claims can be complex and it is important to instruct an experienced solicitor.</p>\r\n<h2>Untraced motorist</h2>\r\n<p>Even if the motorist failed to stop and you were unable to obtain the registration number of the vehicle, a claim can be pursued against the Motor Insurers Bureau under the &ldquo;Untraced Drivers Agreement&rdquo;.&nbsp; It is a condition, however, that the accident be reported to the Police within 5 days of the incident, if claiming for property damage, or within 14 days if claiming for personal injuries. Failure to do so will jeopardise a claim.</p>\r\n<p>If you think you have a claim then call us now for a <strong>free assessment </strong>of your case.&nbsp; Our advice is FREE and you will get to keep 100% of any compensation awarded to you.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>','2011-05-09 14:40:56','2011-05-20 10:44:57','','',2,1,0,NULL,1,0,'<p>We can help</p>\r\n<p>Call now 0333 200 2311</p>','32_broken_leg.JPG','image/jpeg',105363,'2011-05-13 13:15:48','','family_highlight',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','RoadTrafficAccidents.jpg','image/jpeg',28269,'2011-05-20 10:44:56','Road Traffic Accidents','','','Road Traffic Accidents','','',2,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(140,'Slips and Trips','slips_and_trips','Slips and Trips',135,0,0,1,'2010-04-29 08:55:42','<div id=\"pane1\" class=\"tabPaneOn\">\r\n<div class=\"cmsContent\">\r\n<h2>We\'re with you every step of the way</h2>\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;ve fallen and injured yourself, we can advise as to whether you might have&nbsp;a slip injury claim. We&rsquo;ve successfully helped people recover compensation after slips in supermarkets, restaurants, shops, pubs and many other locations.</p>\r\n<p>The owners or occupiers of public or commercial premises have a duty of care to ensure your safety. If your accident happened on their premises and we can prove they failed in that duty, we should be able to make a strong case for a slip injury compensation claim.</p>\r\n<p>Our team&nbsp;specialise in accident claims involving slipping/tripping injuries. If they think that you have a right to pursue a claim, we&rsquo;ll do everything we can to help you get the compensation you deserve.</p>\r\n<p>Not only that, but if your slip injuries are such that you&rsquo;re incapacitated, they&rsquo;ll ensure you get the right rehabilitation support to help you get back on an even keel.</p>\r\n<p>If you slipped in a shop, pub or other public place, try and take photos of the area where you slipped. This will help us to prove that someone else was at fault for your accident. You should also make sure that your slip is recorded in the accident book if applicable. It is also useful to collect the names and addresses of any witnesses who can help to piece together what happened.</p>\r\n<h2>Accidents in Public Places</h2>\r\n<p>Every year in the UK, thousands of people are injured due to an accident in a public place. Most recover from their injuries with time but the knock-on effect for others can mean long term disability, ongoing pain and continuing financial losses. If you have been injured as a result of an accident in a public place, such as a trip, slip or fall, then you could be entitled to make an accident claim to compensate you for your injuries.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Thousands of people every year experience some form of accident in a public place for which they could make an accident compensation claim. This could be the result of a trip, slip, fall or being struck by falling objects.</p>\r\n<p>The responsibility for the accident will often lie with the owner of the premises or property in which the accident took place or the local authority responsible for maintaining public spaces. They have a legal responsibility known as a \"duty of care\" to minimise the risk of accidents and where we can prove you were injured because that duty was breached, we&rsquo;ll pursue an accident compensation claim on your behalf.</p>\r\n<p>Call us now if you think you might have a claim or e-mail <a href=\"mailto:claims@bannerjones.co.uk\">claims@bannerjones.co.uk</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','2011-05-09 15:04:28','2011-05-20 10:43:11','','',2,1,0,NULL,1,0,'<p>Call us now on 0333 200 2311</p>\r\n<p>or click here to email <a href=\"mailto:claim@bannerjones.co.uk\">claim@bannerjones.co.uk</a></p>','32_broken_leg.JPG','image/jpeg',105363,'2011-05-13 13:43:32','','family_highlight',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','SlipsAndTrips.jpg','image/jpeg',29372,'2011-05-20 10:43:11','Slips and Trips','','','Slips and Trips','','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(141,'Accidents at Work','accidents_at_work','Accidents at Work',136,0,0,1,'2010-04-29 08:55:42','<div id=\"c3581\" class=\"csc\">\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<p class=\"teaser\">The HSE has stated that are 150,000 non-fatal injuries being reported each year whilst, sadly, 200 people lost their lives due to an accident or injury at work.&nbsp; In additional it is estimated that 2 million people suffer from ill health caused or exacerbated by accidents and injury at work.&nbsp; Whilst some of these injuries are minor, some have more serious consequences such as time off work, financial and emotional strain or even permanent disability.&nbsp; Whatever your circumstances, we\'ll be with you every step of the way.</p>\r\n<p class=\"teaser\">Compensation can go a long way to ease the burden that an accident and injury at work has caused and choosing the right solicitor for your case is one of the most important decisions you&rsquo;ll have to make.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"teaser\">There are many types of accident and injury suffered at work that you may be able to claim compensation for.&nbsp; Below are just a selection of the ones our team&nbsp;of injury solicitors will be able to help with:</p>\r\n<div class=\"teaser\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Accidents on Building/Construction sites</li>\r\n<li>Mesothelioma Claims and other Asbestos related diseases</li>\r\n<li>Loss of hearing</li>\r\n<li>Hand Arm Vibration Syndrome</li>\r\n<li>Skin conditions</li>\r\n<li>Severe injuries resulting in amputation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Call us now for your free no obligation chat on 0333 200 231. You get to keep 100% of any compensation awarded to you.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','2011-05-09 15:31:15','2011-05-20 10:42:54','','',2,1,0,NULL,1,0,'<p>We can help you</p>\r\n<p>0333 200 2311</p>\r\n<p>Free no obligation advice</p>','4_AccreditedPersonalInjury.jpg','image/jpeg',31123,'2011-05-13 13:22:01','','family_highlight',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','AccidentsAtWork.jpg','image/jpeg',34262,'2011-05-20 10:42:54','Accidents at Work','','','Accidents at Work','','',2,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(142,'Work Related Illness','work_related_illness','Work Related Illness',137,0,0,1,'2010-04-29 08:55:42','<p>Employers have a responsibility to protect their employees from work related accidents and illnesses.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;When this protection is missing or flawed, serious personal injury or even death can result and you may be entitled to a compensation claim.</p>\r\n<p>Some of the more common work related illnesses included:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Asbestos related diseases</li>\r\n<li>Carpal tunnel syndrome</li>\r\n<li>Acoustic shock / hearing loss</li>\r\n<li>Vibration white finger</li>\r\n<li>Repetitive strain </li>\r\n<li>Occupational Asthma</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>If you think you have a claim then please give our experts a call for a free initial assessment of your case.&nbsp; Call us on 0333 200 2311 or e-mail <a href=\"mailto:claim@bannerjones.co.uk\">claim@bannerjones.co.uk</a></p>','2011-05-09 15:48:08','2011-05-20 10:45:01','','',2,1,0,NULL,1,0,'<p>Free Initial Advice</p>\r\n<p>0333 200 2311</p>','4_AccreditedPersonalInjury.jpg','image/jpeg',31123,'2011-05-13 13:50:14','','family_highlight',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','WorkRelatedIllness.jpg','image/jpeg',35678,'2011-05-20 10:45:00','Work Related Illness','','','Work Related Illness','','',2,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(143,'Medical Negligence','medical_negligence','Medical Negligence',138,0,0,1,'2010-04-29 08:55:42','<p>We are lucky in that the healthcare system in this country is of a high standard and&nbsp;generally we&nbsp;place a lot of trust in our doctors, dentists, nurses and other health care professionals.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Sometimes things do go wrong however, and you may find yourself if a situation where you are eligible to make a claim.</p>\r\n<p>If you have been a victim of a medical accident, in the NHS or privately, and that accident is due to incompetent care or lack of judgement by a healthcare professional, it may be possible to bring a claim for medical negligence compensation.&nbsp; &nbsp;Medical negligence claims can be difficult to prove, so it is vital that you seek expert legal advice on your case as soon as possible.</p>\r\n<p>These are often sensitive and difficult claims and you can be assured we will handle your case in a sympathetic manner, listen carefully to what you want to achieve and provide the best advice to meet your needs.</p>\r\n<p>Some of the areas we can seek claims against are:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>GP negligence</li>\r\n<li>Accident and Emergency </li>\r\n<li>Anaesthetic errors</li>\r\n<li>Nerve Injuries</li>\r\n<li>Hospital negligence</li>\r\n<li>Birth Injuires</li>\r\n<li>Amputation errors</li>\r\n<li>Pressure sores</li>\r\n<li>Surgery errors</li>\r\n<li>Care home neglect</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>If you think you may have a case then why not call one of our specialist personal injury solicitors today on 0333 200 2311?&nbsp; Your case assessment if Free and there is no obligation to take things any further.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2011-05-09 15:54:51','2011-05-20 10:44:52','','',2,1,0,NULL,1,0,'<p>For a free no obligation chat</p>\r\n<p>call us now on</p>\r\n<p>0333 200 2311</p>','4_AccreditedPersonalInjury.jpg','image/jpeg',31123,'2011-05-13 13:31:30','','family_highlight',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','MedicalNegligence.jpg','image/jpeg',32741,'2011-05-20 10:44:52','Medical Negligence','','','Medical Negligence','','',2,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(144,'Defective Products','defective_products','Defective Products',139,0,0,1,'2010-04-29 08:55:42','<p>If you have suffered ill health as a result of using a defective product then Banner Jones can help you every step of the way.&nbsp; Whether the injuries you have suffered are physical, emotional, and financial or a combination of all three, we understand and can help you get the compensation you deserve.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>All of your discussions are confidential so please don\'t be embarrassed to&nbsp;get in touch&nbsp;so that we can&nbsp;help you to obtain the evidence you need to make a claim. You have the right to compensation.</p>\r\n<p>We act on behalf of clients who have&nbsp;have suffered an injury as a result of a&nbsp;defective products including:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Toys, electrical goods or even items of furniture</li>\r\n<li>Hair dyes and cosmetics</li>\r\n<li>Foriegn bodies found in food items</li>\r\n<li>Defective drugs like thalidomide, vioxx, statins, opren, benzodiazapines, aspirin and human growth hormone </li>\r\n<li>Defective medical items such as Breast and corneal implants or Contraceptive devices </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>We&rsquo;ll do everything we can&nbsp;to get what you deserve from the manufacturer&nbsp;and ensure you&rsquo;re awarded maximum compensation for your suffering.</p>\r\nCall us today for a no obligation confidential chat about your injury on 0333 200 2311','2011-05-09 15:55:52','2011-05-20 10:44:29','','',2,1,0,NULL,1,0,'<p>Start your claim today</p>\r\n<p>No Win No Fee</p>\r\n<p>You keep 100% of any compensation</p>','101_iStock_000012189698XSmall.jpg','image/jpeg',99626,'2011-05-13 13:33:40','','family_highlight',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','DefectiveProducts.jpg','image/jpeg',34160,'2011-05-20 10:44:28','Defective Products','','','Defective Products','/web/contact_us','',2,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(145,'Accident Claim Centre','accident_claim_centre','Accident Claim Centre',140,0,0,1,'