hers and healthcare and other professionals from a wide range of disciplines.\r\nRachel advises and represents clients from investigation through to formal proceedings.','What some of her clients have said :\r\n\r\n\"Rachel’s highly professional approach and reasonable charges were a great bonus. I valued her detailed, honest advice and guidance and prompt responses throughout\"\r\n\r\n\"Being available out of hours was invaluable to me at the most critical time when deadlines were looming\"\r\n\r\n\"The personal touch coupled with her experience and sensible approach made all the difference when dealing with something so complicated and upsetting.  I had almost given up hope of retaining my ability to practise\"\r\n\r\n\"It was a pleasure having her on my side and could not have got through it without the expert help and guidance.\r\nI could not fault the service I received and we were ready well in advance!\"\r\n','She is a member of the Law Society and Lincoln’s Inn.  \r\n\r\nRachel is also a member of the Association of Regulatory and Disciplinary Lawyers.','Waitress at a golf club','Walking the dog, home interiors, cooking, gardening and films','Depending on the time of day - cappuccino or chardonnay','In winter - somewhere in the southern hemisphere- where there is no phone reception','Turning 40 and having a party to remember followed by a trip to New York',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',''),(53,'John Nettleship','Paralegal ','jn@bannerjones.co.uk','01246 560527','Glumangate ','2012-04-18 12:46:43','2012-05-14 11:35:13',2,1,0,NULL,1,23,'John Nettleship.JPG','image/pjpeg',21365,'2012-05-01 11:56:54','','JohnNettleshipBubble.jpg','image/jpeg',21292,'2012-05-14 11:35:13','','University of Sheffield','','John works in our Wills and Probate Department and specialises in Wills writing. John runs the free Legal Advice Clinic that Banner Jones hosts for Age Concern in Chesterfield every week at their premises.\r\n','','','Pensions Administrator at Norwich Union','I love to play the piano and I try to make time to read as often as I can','Strawberry milkshake','A road trip across the US or Europe would be fantastic','Getting a distinction on my LPC',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',''),(54,'Bob Sowter','Solicitor','rds@bannerjones.co.uk','01246 283009','Marsden Street','2012-04-18 13:02:18','2012-05-30 14:52:49',2,1,0,NULL,1,22,'168_Bob Sowter large.JPG','image/jpeg',104287,'2012-05-09 08:39:53','','RobertSowterBubble.jpg','image/jpeg',57037,'2012-05-30 14:52:49','','Bob studied for his Bachelors at the University of Manchester and for my Masters at Sheffield University.','Qualified in 2010.','Criminal Defence representing clients at the police station and the Magistrates Court on a daily basis.\r\n','','Bob is a member of the Law Society’s Criminal Litigation Panel\r\n','Paper round','Walking, running, playing squash, and snowboarding','Tea during the day and red wine in the evening','Snowboarding in deep snow and bright sunshine','Walking the Inca trail in Peru\r\n\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',''),(55,'Serena Mendies','Trainee Costs Draftsperson','sm@bannerjones.co.uk','01246 560548 ','Glumangate','2012-05-09 10:25:27','2012-05-23 10:17:18',2,2,0,NULL,1,38,'Serena large.JPG','image/pjpeg',154632,'2012-05-09 10:26:34','','SerenaMendiesBubble.jpg','image/jpeg',21637,'2012-05-14 11:33:56','','University of Lancaster & College of Law in Chester','','Serena has a Law Degree.','','','Office Clerk at Co-Operative Insurance','Visiting and socializing with friends as much as I can. Reading and music','Strawberry Ribena','A trip to see the Northern Lights in Norway','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'',''),(56,'Stacey Lee','Paralegal','sl@bannerjones.co.uk','01246 562082','Bolsover','2012-09-12 11:39:44','2012-09-18 14:19:22',2,1,0,NULL,1,39,'stacey small 2012.J