INSERT INTO `testimonials` VALUES (1,'The service I received couldn\'t have been better! ','Mrs C, Chesterfield ','2010-11-18 13:28:05','2011-09-30 12:45:18',1,1,0,NULL,1,0),(2,'It just goes for me to say thank you for your help and assistance and especially the advice in this matter and should A2Z have the need for similar services.  We will certainly consider Banner Jones first				\r\n','A2Z computers, London ','2010-12-09 10:25:16','2011-02-10 16:34:07',1,2,0,NULL,1,0),(3,'If in future I need legal advice my preference will be with Banner Jones after such great service','Mr Kingston','2010-12-09 10:25:54','2011-02-10 16:34:50',1,2,0,NULL,1,0),(4,'Thank you again for your help..If anyone requires a solicitor at any time..I will recommend yourselves..for quick and friendly service				\r\n','Miss N, Chesterfield','2010-12-09 10:26:10','2011-02-10 16:35:32',1,2,0,NULL,1,0),(5,'Thank You so much for your help and support through this difficult time, the collaborative process worked well for us				\r\n','Mrs W, Sheffield','2011-01-25 10:34:33','2011-02-10 16:36:06',2,2,0,NULL,1,0),(6,'The service I received was excellent.','Mrs B, Dronfield','2011-02-10 16:36:37','2011-02-10 16:36:37',2,NULL,0,NULL,1,0),(7,'I received excellent service for the purchase of my house','Mrs S,Sheffield','2011-02-10 16:37:42','2011-03-01 12:42:59',2,2,0,NULL,1,0),(8,'Mr Barlow was a gentleman on both visits to my home and I would recommend him.\r\n','Mrs B, Chesterfield','2011-02-28 14:00:25','2011-02-28 14:00:25',2,NULL,0,NULL,1,0),(9,'I just wanted to say what a fantastic, professional, not to mention fast, job Toni White did preparing my UK will for me. Toni turned around my Will and gave superb advice in just two days for which I am very grateful.  I\'d also like to add that the receptionist staff on both days we visited your office were extremely friendly and the whole experience of dealing with Banner Jones was wonderful.  ','Tracey Howard','2011-02-28 14:00:56','2011-02-28 14:51:51',2,2,0,NULL,1,0),(10,'The receptionist staff on both days we visited your office were extremely friendly and the whole experience of dealing with Banner Jones was wonderful','T Howard','2011-02-28 14:02:12','2011-02-28 14:02:12',2,NULL,0,NULL,1,0),(11,'All though you are now part of Banner-Jones, to me you are still Glossops, and the service we receive is part of why we have been with you for so many years.','Mr T Pass','2011-04-20 15:39:51','2011-04-20 15:39:51',2,NULL,0,NULL,1,0),(12,'All is oustanding! \r\n','Miss C Chesterfield','2011-04-20 15:40:44','2011-09-30 11:57:39',2,2,0,NULL,1,0),(13,'Thankyou Helena Downing for all your excellent service.  You are a credit to the firm. Kind Regards','Mr & Mrs W Alfreton','2011-07-19 08:37:57','2011-09-30 11:51:50',2,2,0,NULL,1,0),(14,'Thank you for everything that you have done to help us move house very quickly & smoothly','Miss R & Mr D','2011-07-19 08:38:42','2011-09-30 11:52:35',2,2,0,NULL,1,0),(15,'I just wanted to say thank you so very much for all the help I was given when I needed advice very quickly. Richard Barlow (Chesterfield ) and Catherine (Dronfield) were so kind, understanding and helpful. My first impresssions of Banner Jones are outstanding and I will not hesitate to contact you in the near future when I will require futher assistance. Normally I may feel a little intimidated speaking to a solicitor but was made to feel really at ease.','Mrs A, Chesterfield','2011-07-19 08:39:22','2011-09-30 11:53:01',2,2,0,NULL,1,0),(16,'I was involved in an accident and my insurance company thought they had achieved the world for me by getting an offer of 50/50. This offer would mean not only would I get 50% of the damage done to my car, but would also lose my no claims bonus. I went to Banner Jones with all the paperwork and just a few weeks later I was banking a cheque for the full amount of damages and had my no claims discount. Great Service!','Mr M Bates, Chesterfield','2011-09-30 11:48:07','2011-09-30 11:55:24',2,2,0,NULL,1,0),(17,'I would like to put on record my great appreciation of the efficient manner in which you have dealt with the estate.  At all times you have been so helpful and your advice when things seemed to be falling apart has minimised my stress level.','Mr S, Sheffield','2011-11-23 11:17:11','2011-11-23 11:17:11',2,NULL,0,NULL,1,0),(18,'\"I am very grateful for all your efforts and a very satisfactory result.  I cannot thank you enough for a first class service and I will happily recommend you to my friends and family\" ','Mr W, Nottingham','2012-04-10 10:52:56','2012-04-10 10:52:56',2,NULL,0,NULL,1,0),(19,'I would like to put on record my great appreciation of the efficient manor in which you have dealt with the estate.  At all times you have been so helpful and your advice when things seemed to be falling apart has minimised my stress level.  I have ensured tha members of the family, with whom I have contact, know the value of your contribution to settling my aunts financial affairs.  It has been a great pleasure working with you and I shall keep in touch when necessary.\r\n','Mr S, Sheffield','2012-05-01 12:26:18','2012-05-01 12:28:30',2,2,0,NULL,1,0),(20,'Rachel Barlow has just completed the legal arrangements in respect of my divorce.  The service I received was exemplary and I wanted to write to you to let you know this.  I have been pretty constrained in relation to availablity to meet and most of our business has been done over email which I appreciated, responses have been very timely, updates provided regularly, deadlines hit and fees reasonable.  I contrast this with the service provided by a large law firm in sheffield in the early part of the year and your approach and that of your staff to customer services, in my , sets your firm apart.  Your firm, and Rachel in particular, came to me though personal recommendation by and friend and I shall be happy to do the same.  As I said to Rachel I am fully aware that those working with the public ( I work for the nhs) receive alot of brickbars than bouquets, so I wanted to let you know how happy I have been with the service received.  Thank you again.\r\n','Mr C Sheffield','2012-05-01 12:31:43','2012-05-01 12:31:43',2,NULL,0,NULL,1,0),(21,'Thanks for your assistance with my case, your advise has been invaluable, and I would certainly recommend Banner Jones to my family and friends.\r\n','Mr P Sheffield','2012-05-01 12:32:34','2012-05-01 12:32:34',2,NULL,0,NULL,1,0),(22,'Thank you very much for your kind assistance and will certainly use your service in the future.\r\n','Mr L Derbyshire','2012-05-01 12:33:23','2012-05-01 12:33:23',2,NULL,0,NULL,1,0),(23,'We would like to thank our solicitor acting for us Richard, he did  a great job and was very easy to speak to and very friendly.  Extremley professional and we would use him again in the future.\r\n','Mr & Mrs S, Sheffield','2012-05-01 12:34:17','2012-05-01 12:34:17',2,NULL,0,NULL,1,0),(24,'I am very grateful for all your efforts and a very satisfactory result.  I cannot thank youenough for a frist class service and I will happily recommend you to my friends and family\"\r\n','Mr W, Nottingham','2012-05-01 12:35:06','2012-05-01 12:36:23',2,2,0,NULL,1,0),(25,'I would like to take the opportunity of thanking you for your services and i can now start to move on with my life.\r\n','Mr F, Chesterfield','2012-05-01 12:37:00','2012-05-01 12:37:00',2,NULL,0,NULL,1,0),(26,'The advice Kevin gave me was good, he was easy to contact, I am a very happy client','Miss Z, Nottingham','2012-07-10 10:22:25','2012-07-10 10:22:25',2,NULL,0,NULL,1,0),(27,'I have been using the Banner Jones Costs drafting team to prepare my legal aid bills, for over a year.  I find their service to be extremely prompt, accurate and cost effective.  They are always happy to answer my queries, and discuss issues that arise.\r\n\r\nOne big advantage is that, as solicitors themselves, they understand the problems that high street firms face in dealing with public funding issues and are able to offer straightforward practical advice.\r\n\r\nI have been very impressed with the work they have done for me and would recommend them very highly.\r\n\r\n','Mr P Jones Dean Thomas & Co Worksop','2012-08-07 11:19:03','2012-08-07 11:19:03',2,NULL,0,NULL,1,0);
